@prefix : <#> .
@prefix s: <http://www.nongnu.org/samizdat/rdf/schema#> .

# RDF Namespaces
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

# Standard Tags
:Quality
	a s:Tag ;
	rdfs:comment "Overall quality of the resource." .

:Priority
	a s:Tag ;
	rdfs:comment "Importance of the resource to site members." .

:Relevance
	a s:Tag ;
	rdfs:comment "Shows how much content of the resource is related to the enclosing aggregate resource; low Relevance highlights off-topic resources." .

# Optional Tags
:Fairness
	a s:Tag ;
	rdfs:comment "Whether resource fairly represents all sides of the story." .

:Representation
	a s:Tag ;
	rdfs:comment "Readability, quality of prose, cinematics, etc." .

:Factuality
	a s:Tag ;
	rdfs:comment "Extent of sources usage vs. speculation." .

:Novelty
	a s:Tag ;
	rdfs:comment "Whether resource adds anything new to the body of information (low Novelty highlights redundant resources)." .

:FrontPage
	a s:Tag ;
	rdfs:comment "Whether resource is worthy of adding to the site's default front page." .

# Versioning-specific Tags
:Correction
	a s:Tag ;
	rdfs:comment "Minor correction that doesn't change structure or meaning." .

:Rewrite
	a s:Tag ;
	rdfs:comment "Full rewrite of the message." .

:Summary
	a s:Tag ;
	rdfs:comment "Short digest or summary of this and possibly other messages." .

:Translation
	a s:Tag ;
	rdfs:comment "Translation to a different language." .

:Mirror
	a s:Tag ;
	rdfs:comment "Alternative location of the message." .

# Member Tags
:Friendship
	a s:Tag ;
	rdfs:comment "Overall friendship towards a member." .

